{"tid":1775273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【運動正式踏入半年】我係一個和理非，我有嘢想講！！","createTime":"2019-12-08T17:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:01:52.000Z","uid":231234,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d95eb2b318edba5cafbb0efa42f5b1a25f56ff43","tid":1775273,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"首先，我想同大家講句<strong> 多謝！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月9到依家，話咁快就過半年，多謝所有以唔同形式參與過今場運動嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢半年發生咗好多嘢，發生咗好多我冇諗過嘅嘢<br />\n由100萬，200萬+1，612通宵留守，71立法會一個都不能少，<br />\n人鏈、車手幫手塞路變rb、「和你 系列活動」...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經，我好自私咁諗過，自己參加完100萬&amp;200萬+1遊行之後，就唔再出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係，我見到各位手足，特別係勇武流咗唔少血，先換取到暫緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武唔少都係中學生，後生仔，我就知道自己唔可以咁自私<br />\n所以暫緩之後，仲陸續有參加唔同形式嘅行動，直到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n呢半年，我見到真．香港人真係好犀利，喺呢場冇大台嘅運動<br />\n有好多無條件付出嘅手足，勇武、和理非、FA、文宣、冷氣軍師、街坊、黃店、<br />\n物資站、家長義載、飯券、國際戰線、人權法戰線......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日，我諗過出唔出嚟好，一嚟本身仲病病地，二嚟又俾fd賣咗，得自己一個<br />\n諗咗陣，身為一個和理非，民陣吹雞又難得有不反，緊係要出一分力啦，難為勇武仲要打生打死，冒住被捕、被消失風險，自己作為一個和理非冇得唔出嚟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我今日遲到，但都由起點行到終點，返緊去嗰陣見到今日有80萬人出嚟<br />\n老實講，係有失落過，我以為今日咁多人，行緊個個都話今日點都有100萬人<br />\n見到最後公佈係80萬人，但喺我心目中係有100萬人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日遊行真係好開心，好耐冇試過參加有不反嘅大型民陣遊行，由日頭行到天黑，望住手足塞爆成條街，一盞盞手機嘅燈光，我真係感受到大家冇放棄，見到大家仲堅持緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想多謝咁多位手足，不論你今日有出嚟行，定係休息冇出，或係因為被捕定各種原因出唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動，我哋可以休息，<strong>但唔可以放棄，要用各種形式參加行動</strong>，twitter又好，文宣，推post，做軍師又好，要繼續參加，因為呢個係我哋生於亂世嘅責任！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>毋忘去世/受傷/流忘手足，<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>繼續不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時見到大家唔會過份美化自己人嘅缺點，<br />\n無論遮樣方式又好，避免陣地轉型咗去快閃又好，識得要靜靜地贏又好，<br />\n以前唔覺意犯咗嘅錯大家會檢討，避免再次犯錯，因為我哋大家都進化緊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"039ccd6bc45ac10dc75eea331f22829e04205b4c","tid":1775273,"uid":116054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好同黑警談判，接受任何政府條件，一定要堅持落去，直到每一個手足無事"},{"pid":"350c97b8d3acd2cde1d0e4ce0c7570362105878c","tid":1775273,"uid":327681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:05:46.000Z","msg":"今日我條腰痛到仆街。仲要喺百德新街塞咗個半鐘頭，我都堅持行到去終點。和勇一家，一齊繼續努力！"},{"pid":"96b7b52e6ad1d8d8cdab735be2c6120cd071924e","tid":1775273,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce419f39098767a03aef3b247cb820e774d488ad","tid":1775273,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6da05f9e0ba969a6ceb0763802028c98f967e9","tid":1775273,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:29:17.000Z","msg":"我見起碼1-2成人係單拖"},{"pid":"d8ee99ae83945a1f6a103d5f3b3d8bc711a57e4e","tid":1775273,"uid":63912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea6da05f9e0ba969a6ceb0763802028c98f967e9","tid":1775273,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:29:17.000Z","msg":"我見起碼1-2成人係單拖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"單拖有單拖好處 唔洗等鐘意遲到既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋行動力會高d 但相對體力消耗都快d"},{"pid":"d440e79a4a2ed2fa7479fcbcd6f357ecab2f7905","tid":1775273,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6b0b8f04a298e971a16aacd9ed7cfd427fb612","tid":1775273,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"039ccd6bc45ac10dc75eea331f22829e04205b4c","tid":1775273,"uid":116054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score